<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَنْ يَسكُنَ فِيهِ الشَّيْطَانْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لاَ تَخْشَ خُيُولَ أَبِي بَكْرٍ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
